Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.40,1:22:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It gave neuroscsychiatric confirmation\Nof what we've been teaching about
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.08,1:22:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,intention. You think\Nneurossychiatrically it's been
