Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.04,1:26:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NI get that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.23,1:26:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I just wanted to share those with you.\NThank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.23,1:26:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes, I like it.\N>> Great. Yeah, they were nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.52,1:26:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Visitors from other dimensions.\N>> Angelic visitors.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.19,1:26:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you. Okay.\N>> Sometimes they have to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.23,1:26:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they can you can let them\Nrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.36,1:26:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> My question is about um karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.12,1:27:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And here in the United States, I think\Nmost people when you say the word karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.44,1:27:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they mean the sum total of all the\Nkarmic merit or demerit we've acrewed
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.00,1:27:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,during the course of our life. What we\Ndo. But when I was reading about karm
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.76,1:27:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic theory, I saw the mention of two\Nother types of karma. One being the um
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.15,1:27:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the planet earth has its own karma. And\Nsometimes we have acts of nature that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.71,1:27:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,affect us and that seems that seems\Npretty um pretty reasonable. But the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.52,1:27:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,third type of karma that's been\Nmentioned in my reading is group karma
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.80,1:27:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where the activities initiated by others\Ncan forcefully impinge on your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.08,1:27:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> So that things can happen to you that
