Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.36,1:27:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Sure.\N>> They're more about the karma of the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.84,1:28:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,people\N>> doing it. And it's really um just that
