Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.88,1:28:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> and it happened to you.\N>> Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.04,1:28:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So you agree?\N>> Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.88,1:28:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.\N>> Yes. Is group karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.52,1:28:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> See just by agreement with the culture\Nyou now have you know for better or
