Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.84,1:28:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, people forget that it can be\Nfor better,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.00,1:28:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> right? Group consciousness can\N>> group
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.88,1:28:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> really affect Yeah.\N>> our lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.36,1:28:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> Thank you.
